Q4---------------------------------------------

Best Case: O(1)

Worst Case: O(log n)

Challenge------------------------------------------------------

```python
def binary_search(arr, target):
    left = 0
    right = len(arr)-1

    while(left <= right):

        mid = (left + right)//2

        if arr[mid] == target:
            return mid

        elif arr[mid] > target:
            right = mid -1

        else:
            left = mid + 1

    return -1

arr = [2,4,6,5,9,10,34,67]

target = 7

result = binary_search(arr, target)

print(result)
```

